Angel Prime/Depth Charge/Jazz/Gold 
Bug/Metalwarhawk/Tigerhawk/Rhinox/Cheetor








Angel Prime moves out of the way of the missles and lauched a small 
energy blast at Banzi-Tron. He fired it in a shape of a ball.




~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~


Depth Charge,Rhinox,Cheetor,Tigerhawk walk to the new city.



~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~


Jazz and Gold bug walk into the new bridge of the autobot ship.


Gold Bug: "well I am going to set all my stuff up in my room."

Jazz: "ok I will do mine later."


Gold Bug walks to his room and starts setting up his stuff.



~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Metalwarhawk ended the com. He couldn't wait till he got to test his 
tomohawk missles in combat. He arrived at the ship and transformed.
